flowchart LR
    subgraph Source
        A[Developer] --> B[Git Push]
    end

    subgraph CI
        B --> C[Build]
        C --> D{Tests Pass?}
        D -->|Yes| E[Docker Image]
        D -->|No| F[Notify Dev]
        F --> A
    end

    subgraph Deploy
        E --> G{Environment?}
        G -->|Staging| H[Deploy Staging]
        G -->|Production| I[Deploy Prod]
        H --> J{Smoke Tests?}
        J -->|Pass| I
        J -->|Fail| K[Rollback]
    end
